## Layer Caching

### Optimize Build Order

```dockerfile
# GOOD: Dependencies change less often than code
COPY package*.json ./
RUN npm ci                # Cached if package.json unchanged
COPY . .                   # Only this layer rebuilds on code change
RUN npm run build

# BAD: Code change invalidates npm install cache
COPY . .
RUN npm ci
RUN npm run build
```

### Use .dockerignore

```
# .dockerignore
node_modules
npm-debug.log
dist
.git
.env
*.md
.DS_Store
```

